=== 人類星球畫面造假 ===
2015年，英國媒体报道，《[[人类星球|人类星球]]》在[[沙漠|沙漠]]一期中<ref>{{cite web |title=Missing desert camel |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00dds53 |website=BBC |accessdate=2022-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222103206/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00dds53 |archivedate=2016-02-22 |language=en |dead-url=yes}}</ref>，用半驯化的[[狼|狼]]代替了野狼拍攝，两个[[蒙古|蒙古]]牧民冲着[[戈壁|戈壁]]上的野狼开枪是排練的假動作<ref name="qdaily">{{cite web |author1=周哲浩 |title=BBC 承认纪录片《人类星球》造假，为了拍摄而搭建树屋 |url=https://www.qdaily.com/articles/51927.html |website=好奇心日报 |accessdate=2022-06-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180411224338/http://www.qdaily.com/articles/51927.html |archivedate=2018-04-11 |language=zh-cn |dead-url=no}}</ref>。BBC之後承認，该片制片人无法为节目拍摄野狼，而使用了一只半驯化的狼，許多狼跑過鏡頭的動作是狼跑向畫面外的馴養員。这组镜头误导了观众，严重违反了编辑准则<ref>{{cite news |author1=Elizabeth Rigby |title=Another howler for BBC film makers |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/another-howler-for-bbc-film-makers-ml8wj666nhb |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]] |date=2015-10-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.ph/ILo5R |archivedate=2021-07-18 |language=en |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=BBC Annual Report and Accounts 2015/16 |url=https://downloads.bbc.co.uk/aboutthebbc/insidethebbc/reports/pdf/bbc-annualreport-201516.pdf |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2022-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804030922/https://downloads.bbc.co.uk/aboutthebbc/insidethebbc/reports/pdf/bbc-annualreport-201516.pdf |archivedate=2016-08-04 |page=29-30 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=BBC Trust: Nature documentaries broke accuracy rules |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35611222 |website=BBC |accessdate=2022-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202130845/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35611222 |archivedate=2020-12-02 |language=en |date=2016-02-19 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年4月，BBC发表声明，《[[人類星球|人類星球]]》与[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]原住民[[科罗威人|科罗威人]]有关的一集中，部落搬进树屋，并在那里安家的描述并不准确，相关场景有误导性，违反了编辑准则<ref>{{cite web |title=Statement regarding Human Planet |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/statements/human-planet |website=BBC |accessdate=2022-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220512123128/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/statements/human-planet |archivedate=2022-05-12 |language=en |date=2018-04-04 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Human Planet: Tribe's treehouses not real home, says BBC |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-43649469 |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=BBC |date=2018-04-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109005439/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-43649469 |archivedate=2020-11-09 |language=en |dead-url=no}}</ref>该集给人的印象是科罗威人会建造非常高的树屋作为居住场所，但他们一般住在离地面更近的树屋，并将较高的树屋用作仪式用途或部落年轻人聚会场所。参与[[BBC_Two|BBC Two]]另一纪录片《My Year With The Tribe》录制的冒险家Will Millard在与部落成员的讨论中发现了这一错误，当地人告诉他，《人类星球》中非常高的树屋不是他们的房子，而是为了拍摄建造的<ref>{{cite news |author1=Patrick Sawer |title=BBC’s Human Planet in fakery row over staged treehouses |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/04/04/bbcs-human-planet-fakery-row-staged-tree-houses/ |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |date=2018-04-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109025456/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/04/04/bbcs-human-planet-fakery-row-staged-tree-houses/ |archivedate=2020-11-09 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Danny De Vaal |title=BBC admits scenes of ‘tree house’ tribe in The Human Planet were FAKED |url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/5975671/bbc-fake-scenes-human-planet/ |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=[[太陽報_(英國)|太陽報]] |date=2018-04-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210615180155/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/5975671/bbc-fake-scenes-human-planet/ |archivedate=2021-06-15 |language=en}}</ref><ref name="qdaily"/>。

2018年4月底，BBC发布声明指出，《人类星球》第一集“海洋”中，一名拉馬萊拉捕鲸人Benjamin Blikololong被认为在用矛捕捉鲸鱼，但“该场景对角色的描述并不准确，尽管相关镜头反映了他们如何捕鲸”<ref name="bbcs2">{{Cite web |title=Further Statement concerning Human Planet natural history series |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/statements/human-planet-oceans |access-date=2022-06-04 |date=2018-04-26 |publisher=BBC |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701222930/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/statements/human-planet-oceans |archive-date=2019-07-01 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=BBC withdraws Human Planet over editorial breach |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-43921200 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2022-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106081214/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-43921200 |archivedate=2021-11-06 |language=en |date=2018-04-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，而用矛刺中鲸鱼的人实际上不是Benjamin<ref>{{cite news |author1=Anita Singh |title=BBC withdraws Human Planet series after whale hunt scenes exposed as more fakery |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/04/26/bbc-withdraws-human-planet-series-whale-hunt-scenes-exposed/ |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |date=2018-04-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119144210/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/04/26/bbc-withdraws-human-planet-series-whale-hunt-scenes-exposed/ |archivedate=2021-01-19 |language=en |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Matthew Moore |title=BBC kills off Human Planet after whale-hunting ‘fakery’ scandal |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/bbc-kills-off-human-planet-after-whale-hunting-fakery-scandal-3s97nszcl |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=泰晤士报 |date=2018-04-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.ph/kyUDF |archivedate=2021-07-25 |language=en}}</ref>。声明还指，BBC已决定停止《人类星球》的发行，等待全面的编辑审查。<ref name="bbcs2"/>

