p-online-form-after-complaints-hit-peak |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当天BBC电视一台的收视率较上周下跌7%，二台观众下跌65%，当晚7点至11点的收视人数仅为34万<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kanter |first1=Jake |title=Blanket Coverage Of Prince Philip’s Death Proves To Be A Big Turn-Off For British TV Viewers |url=https://deadline.com/2021/04/prince-philip-ratings-death-turn-off-british-viewers-1234731536/ |website=Deadline |accessdate=2021-04-14 |date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210615084504/https://deadline.com/2021/04/prince-philip-ratings-death-turn-off-british-viewers-1234731536/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 塔拉·哈拉瓦 ===
