=== 2021年7月河南水灾報導 ===
2021年7月中旬，河南多地遭遇特大暴雨，郑州等城市发生严重[[2021年7月河南水灾|内涝灾害]]，BBC报道指，郑州曾投资超过500亿元人民币建设“海绵城市”，而这场暴雨“似乎打破了这个神话”。《[[环球时报|环球时报]]》隔日引述观察人士报道批评外国媒体对洪水的报道。<ref>{{cite news |title=河南水災：特大暴雨致數十人死亡 最初24小時發生了什麼 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-57912990 |accessdate=2022-06-04 |work=BBC News 中文 |date=2021-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009134044/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-57912990 |archivedate=2021-10-09 |language=zh-hant |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chinese experts refute BBC report claiming Zhengzhou floods broke sponge city myth - Global Times|url=https://www.globaltimes.cn/page/202107/1229477.shtml|access-date=2021-07-27|work=www.globaltimes.cn|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727165417/https://www.globaltimes.cn/page/202107/1229477.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月22日夜晚，BBC记者白洛宾（Robin Brant）來到鄭州地鐵5號線經開中心廣場站出口報道<ref>{{cite news |title=河南水灾：BBC记者抵达郑州，这座城市地下和地面到底发生了什么 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-57932934 |accessdate=2022-06-03 |work=BBC News 中文 |date=2021-07-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210722142251/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-57932934 |archivedate=2021-07-22 |language=zh-hans |dead-url=no}}</ref>，指過去幾天鄭州市內外不少民衆接到了警告疏散，「但在髒水的臭氣中，一個最令人不安的問题是，為什麼在這條地鐵線上的一個車站，一個建成還不到10年的地鐵系統，會湧入大量雨水，乘客們會被扔在站台上等死。」其中一句「passengers left to die on the platform」在[[BBC中文網|BBC中文網]]被翻譯成「乘客被扔在月台上等死」<ref name="hkc4">{{cite news |author1=王寶熒 |title=外媒採訪雨災遭鄭州市民「喊打喊殺」　內地自媒體稱「失望透頂不再關注河南」 |url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/43705/%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%84-%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E9%9B%A8%E7%81%BD-bbc-43705/ |accessdate=2022-06-03 |work=眾新聞 |date=2021-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120185256/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/43705/%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%84-%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E9%9B%A8%E7%81%BD-bbc-43705/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E9%9B%A8%E7%81%BD%E9%81%AD%E9%84%AD%E5%B7%9E%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8C%E5%96%8A%E6%89%93%E5%96%8A%E6%AE%BA%E3%80%8D-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%87%AA%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B%E9%80%8F%E9%A0%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E3%80%8D |archivedate=2022-01-20 |language=zh-hk |dead-url=no}}</ref>。该段话和影片片段被擷取后在中国大陆网络傳播，引发争议<ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC：“河南暴雨，昼伏夜出，下落不明....”_哔哩哔哩_bilibili|url=https://b23.tv/oV17ra|access-date=2021-07-25|last=新华社|work=b23.tv}}</ref>。《[[參考消息|參考消息]]》24日根据获救市民的采访，指消防员在事故发生后已经尽快赴现场进行救援<ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC造谣“郑州水灾”被喷：这么恶毒的话也说得出口|url=https://mil.sina.cn/2021-07-24/detail-ikqcfnca8825777.d.html|access-date=2021-07-27|date=2021-07-24|last=sina_mobile|work=mil.sina.cn|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727063048/https://mil.sina.cn/2021-07-24/detail-ikqcfnca8825777.d.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。BBC后將报道字幕修改成「乘客死在月台」<ref name="hkc4"/>。[[YouTube_(頻道)|YouTube]]上的该视频遭到中國網民[[洗版|洗版]]，后被删除。白洛宾也从24日起遭到与当地民众发起「人肉围猎」<ref name=":1">{{Cite news |url=https://www.nownews.com/news/5335729 |title=中國網友好氣！BBC記者報導鄭州災情　遭嗆「逮住就打」 |author=詹凌瑀 |work=NOWnews今日新聞 |language=zh-TW |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727051152/https://www.nownews.com/news/5335729 |archivedate=2021-07-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。白洛宾同日在一份报告称「不明白中国人民为何如此脆弱」，并补充说北京已经警告其他地方政府检查自己的准备情况和地铁法规<ref>{{Cite web|title=Foreign journalists harassed by Chinese citizens over Zhengzhou flooding coverage|url=https://hongkongfp.com/2021/07/26/foreign-journalists-harassed-by-chinese-citizens-over-zhengzhou-flooding-coverage/|access-date=2021-07-27|date=2021-07-26|last=Kwan|first=Rhoda|work=Hong Kong Free Press HKFP|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Chinese citizens harass foreign media correspondents over Henan floods coverage|url=https://www.republicworld.com/world-news/china/chinese-citizens-harass-foreign-media-correspondents-over-henan-floods-coverage.html|access-date=2021-07-27|last=World|first=Republic|work=Republic World|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727033349/https://www.republicworld.com/world-news/china/chinese-citizens-harass-foreign-media-correspondents-over-henan-floods-coverage.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该事件进而在7月26日引发了《[[德国之声|德国之声]]》记者与协助同行的《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》驻华记者被民众误认为是BBC记者的围堵乌龙事件，其中[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]和[[有线电视新闻网|美国有线电视新闻网]]的记者同样声称受到[[排外主義|排外主義]]的中国民众在网络上围攻和威胁<ref>{{Cite web|title=Foreign journalists harassed in China over floods coverage|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jul/26/foreign-journalists-harassed-by-chinese-citizens-over-floods-coverage|access-date=2021-07-27|date=2021-07-26|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813154706/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jul/26/foreign-journalists-harassed-by-chinese-citizens-over-floods-coverage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2" />。

=== 誤用吉儀 ===
2022年1月，BBC美食频道应壬寅虎年即将到来，介绍了华人传统美食，其中“鲜虾卤面配花椰菜”的配图出现了答谢出席丧礼亲友的[[吉儀|吉儀]]信封，误将其当成压岁钱，与新年喜庆气氛格格不入，在华人群体中引发争议<ref>{{cite web|title=“寿金当纸巾 吉仪当摆设” BBC与英国卫报错大了|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/20220117/%E5%AF%BF%E9%87%91%E5%BD%93%E7%BA%B8%E5%B7%BE-%E5%90%89%E4%BB%AA%E5%BD%93%E6%91%86%E8%AE%BE-bbc%E4%B8%8E%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%8D%AB%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86/|accessdate=2022-01-18|date=2022-01-17|website=星洲网 Sin Chew Daily}}</ref>。BBC随即在推特发表了道歉声明，并删除了相关配图<ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC and The Guardian Chinese dish recipes showcased with a side of joss paper and funeral envelopes|url=https://www.marketing-interactive.com/bbc-guardian-cny-dishes-mistakes|access-date=2022-01-26|work=www.marketing-interactive.com|language=en-gb}}</ref>。

=== 新闻跑马灯显示“曼联是垃圾”===
2022年5月24日，BBC新闻台的[[字幕跑马灯|字幕跑马灯]]出现了“[[曼联|曼联]]是垃圾”（Manchester United are Rubbish）的侮辱性字样。随后新闻主播安妮塔·麥克維（Annita McVeigh）在稍后的节目中致歉，称有关文字和之后的“到处都在下雨”（Weather Rain Everywhere）由幕后的工作人员随意打出，其目的是熟悉如何打出跑马灯的文字，希望曼联的球迷别生气。<ref>{{cite web |title=BBC apologises after ‘Manchester United are rubbish’ appears on ticker |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2022/may/24/bbc-apologises-after-manchester-united-are-rubbish-appears-on-ticker-news-tennis |website=The Guardian |accessdate=2022-05-24 |date=2022-05-24}}</ref>

